title: Strawberry Lemon By Cloud Nurdz
description: It might give you a strawberry lemonade flavor, but it will be a lot sweeter than you think. This candy flavored e liquid is colliding with some strawberries and lemons to give you the refreshing e liquid called Strawberry Lemon. This e liquid piece of candy is one that will most likely not disappoint because the juicy flavors will make this blend irresistible to most.
